import React from 'react'
import {Row, Col} from 'react-bootstrap'

const CategoryRow= (props)=>{
    return(
        <Row md={4}>
        <Col>
            <CategoryCard category={"Restaurants"} img={restImage} link="restaurants"/>
        </Col>
        <Col xs={6}>
            <CategoryCard category={"Bars"} img={barImage} link="bars"/>
        </Col>
        <Col>
            <CategoryCard category={"Coffee & Tea"} img={coffeeImage} link="coffee"/>
        </Col>
        <Col>
            <CategoryCard category={"Food Trucks"} img={foodtruckImage} link="foodtrucks_more"/>
        </Col>
    </Row>

    )
}

export default CategoryRow;
